findIndexByClassInEclipseView(String, Class, int) - Method in class com.googlecode.swtfinder.core.finder.Finder
this method is used to locate a special Control in an eclipse view with viewID
this method will always try to check if the current active part is the view with viewID,
if it is, it will find the control in this view.
the condition used to find the control is ConditionClassAssignableFind
